<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.6">
<l>ōta mākaṭa laikkaṭan tēṟi yuyarkkoḷ mākkaṭi kāvaiyi ṟuttu</l>
<l>kātal makkaḷum cuṟṟamuṅ koṉṟu kaṭiyi laṅkaima laṅkaye rittut</l>
<l>tūtu vantaku raṅkukkē  yuṅkaḷ tōṉṟal tēviyai viṭṭuko ṭātē</l>
<l>yātar niṉṟupa ṭukiṉṟa tantō vañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having not returned your eminent goddess, releasing [her] to the monkey</l>
<l rend="indent">who came as a messenger,</l>
<l>Having risen up, crossing over the great wavy sea, having cut down</l>
<l rend="indent">the great, fragrant, lofty grove,</l>
<l>Having burned guarded Laṅkā so it was bewildered,</l>
<l rend="indent">and killed [our] beloved family and relatives,</l>
<l>[All of this] keeps happening [to us] fools. Ah, pity! We are frightened.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
